title: Boston Tea Party - Stratford Upon Avon
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Raw, Western, Salad bar, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Bakery, British, English, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Bristol-based chain restaurant. Has an extensive menu; several dishes of which are vegan or could be made vegan. Has all day breakfast, burgers and fries, coffee. A melding of the old school health food cafes and modern coffee bars. Dogs welcome. Free Wi-Fi.
